    "Click Save Credentials, then Test Connection. Lumi stores the values in Keychain and uses them to generate short-lived JWT tokens." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Click Save Credentials, then Test Connection. Lumi stores the values in Keychain and uses them to generate short-lived JWT tokens."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "点击保存凭证，然后测试连接。Lumi 会把这些值存入钥匙串，并用它们生成短期 JWT 令牌。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "按一下儲存憑證，然後測試連線。Lumi 會把這些值存入鑰匙圈，並用它們產生短期 JWT 權杖。"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "按一下儲存憑證，然後測試連線。Lumi 會把這些值存入鑰匙圈，並用它們產生短期 JWT 權杖。"
          }
        },
        "zh-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "按一下儲存憑證，然後測試連線。Lumi 會把這些值存入鑰匙圈，並用它們產生短期 JWT 權杖。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
